SELECT A.DOC_ID ,A.CUST_NO ,B.ITEM_NO ,B.QTY_SOLD ,B.PRC ,C.EMAIL_ADRS_1 as email ,C.FST_NAM as firstname ,C.LST_NAM as lastname ,C.FST_NAM as s_firstname ,C.LST_NAM as s_lastname ,C.CNTRY as s_country ,C.CITY as s_city ,C.STATE as s_state ,C.ZIP_COD as s_zipcode ,C.ADRS_1 as s_address
,C.FST_NAM as b_firstname ,C.LST_NAM as b_lastname ,C.CNTRY as b_country ,C.CITY as b_city ,C.STATE as b_state ,C.ZIP_COD as b_zipcode ,C.ADRS_1 as b_address FROM [dbo].PS_DOC_HDR A inner join PS_DOC_LIN b on a.DOC_ID = b.DOC_ID inner join AR_CUST c on a.CUST_NO = c.CUST_NO

select b.itemno ,b.dim1 ,b.dim2 ,b.dim3 ,b.DIM1_VARIENTID ,b.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM2_VARIENTID ,b.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM3_VARIENTID ,b.DIM3_OPTION_ID ,invcell.LOC_ID from (SELECT one.itemno ,one.dim1 ,one.dim2 ,DIM3.[DIM_3] as dim3 ,one.DIM1_VARIENTID ,one.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,one.DIM2_VARIENTID ,one.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,DIM3.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM3_VARIENTID ,DIM3.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM3_OPTION_ID
FROM ( SELECT DIM1.[ITEM_NO] as itemno ,DIM1.[DIM_1] as dim1 ,DIM2.[DIM_2] as dim2 ,DIM1.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM1_VARIENTID ,DIM1.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM1_OPTION_ID ,DIM2.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM2_VARIENTID ,DIM2.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM2_OPTION_ID
FROM [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_1] DIM1 left join [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_2] DIM2 on DIM1.ITEM_NO = DIM2.ITEM_NO ) AS ONE LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_3] DIM3 ON ONE.itemno = DIM3.ITEM_NO) as b LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_INV_CELL] invcell ON b.itemno = invcell.ITEM_NO

SELECT B.ITEM_NO as ITEM_NO,B.QTY_SOLD as qtysold,B.PRC as prc,C.EMAIL_ADRS_1 as email,C.FST_NAM as firstname,C.LST_NAM as lastname ,C.FST_NAM as s_firstname,C.LST_NAM as s_lastname,C.CNTRY as s_country,C.CITY as s_city,C.STATE as s_state,C.ZIP_COD as s_zipcode ,C.ADRS_1 as s_address,C.FST_NAM as b_firstname,C.LST_NAM as b_lastname,C.CNTRY as b_country,C.CITY as b_city,C.STATE as b_state,C.ZIP_COD as b_zipcode,C.ADRS_1 as b_address FROM [dbo].PS_DOC_HDR A inner join PS_DOC_LIN b on a.DOC_ID = b.DOC_ID inner join AR_CUST c on a.CUST_NO = c.CUST_NO

select b.itemno ,b.dim1 ,b.dim2 ,b.dim3 ,b.DIM1_VARIENTID ,b.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM2_VARIENTID ,b.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM3_VARIENTID ,b.DIM3_OPTION_ID ,invcell.LOC_ID from (SELECT one.itemno ,one.dim1 ,one.dim2 ,DIM3.[DIM_3] as dim3 ,one.DIM1_VARIENTID ,one.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,one.DIM2_VARIENTID ,one.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,DIM3.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM3_VARIENTID ,DIM3.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM3_OPTION_ID
FROM ( SELECT DIM1.[ITEM_NO] as itemno ,DIM1.[DIM_1] as dim1 ,DIM2.[DIM_2] as dim2 ,DIM1.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM1_VARIENTID ,DIM1.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM1_OPTION_ID ,DIM2.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM2_VARIENTID ,DIM2.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM2_OPTION_ID
FROM [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_1] DIM1 left join [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_2] DIM2 on DIM1.ITEM_NO = DIM2.ITEM_NO ) AS ONE LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_3] DIM3 ON ONE.itemno = DIM3.ITEM_NO) as b LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_INV_CELL] invcell ON b.itemno = invcell.ITEM_NO

select b.itemno ,b.dim1 ,b.dim2 ,b.dim3 ,b.DIM1_VARIENTID ,b.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM2_VARIENTID ,b.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,b.DIM3_VARIENTID ,b.DIM3_OPTION_ID ,invcell.LOC_ID from (SELECT one.itemno ,one.dim1 ,one.dim2 ,DIM3.[DIM_3] as dim3 ,one.DIM1_VARIENTID ,one.DIM1_OPTION_ID ,one.DIM2_VARIENTID ,one.DIM2_OPTION_ID ,DIM3.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM3_VARIENTID ,DIM3.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM3_OPTION_ID
FROM ( SELECT DIM1.[ITEM_NO] as itemno ,DIM1.[DIM_1] as dim1 ,DIM2.[DIM_2] as dim2 ,DIM1.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM1_VARIENTID ,DIM1.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM1_OPTION_ID ,DIM2.[USR_VARIANT_ID] AS DIM2_VARIENTID ,DIM2.[USR_OPTION_ID] AS DIM2_OPTION_ID
FROM [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_1] DIM1 left join [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_2] DIM2 on DIM1.ITEM_NO = DIM2.ITEM_NO ) AS ONE LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_GRID_DIM_3] DIM3 ON ONE.itemno = DIM3.ITEM_NO) as b LEFT JOIN [dbo].[IM_INV] invcell ON b.itemno = invcell.ITEM_NO

UPDATE [dbo].IM_GRID_DIM_1 SET DIM_1_UPR = UPPER(DIM_1_UPR) UPDATE [dbo].IM_GRID_DIM_2 SET DIM_2_UPR = UPPER(DIM_2_UPR) UPDATE [dbo].IM_GRID_DIM_3 SET DIM_3_UPR = UPPER(DIM_3_UPR) UPDATE [dbo].IM_INV_CELL SET DIM_1_UPR = UPPER(DIM_1_UPR), DIM_2_UPR = UPPER(DIM_2_UPR), DIM_3_UPR = UPPER(DIM_3_UPR)

UPDATE IM_GRID_DIM_1 SET DIM_1_UPR = UPPER(DIM_1_UPR) UPDATE IM_GRID_DIM_2 SET DIM_2_UPR = UPPER(DIM_2_UPR) UPDATE IM_GRID_DIM_3 SET DIM_3_UPR = UPPER(DIM_3_UPR) UPDATE IM_INV_CELL SET DIM_1_UPR = UPPER(DIM_1_UPR), DIM_2_UPR = UPPER(DIM_2_UPR), DIM_3_UPR = UPPER(DIM_3_UPR)
